All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
AdminController
Controller for Admin page, where admin user can create , list or delete accounts
Album
Class that implements logic of how Albums are created, modified, deleted , as well as how pictures are added/deleted/updated within the album
AlbumController
Controller for Album page, where all albums are listed, can be created, renamed, deleted, and searched by date range ,or tags
InAlbumController
Controller for InAlbum page, handles the functionality of creating, deleting pictures within the album, adding/editing/removing tags and captions for picture, triggering slideshow
LoginController
Controller for Login page, where user can login
NavbarController
Controller for Navigation bar, with buttons common between all pages
Photos
Main Driver class that launches the application
PhotosController
Main controller
PhotosModel  
Picture
Class that implements logic of how Pictures are created, how new tags and captions for pictures are added and modified
PictureController
Implements UI logic on Picture view , handles editing, viewing Picture, adding /deleting tags and captions
Search
This class implements the search for photos in an album, or all user's photos by date range, or tags
SearchController  
SignUpController
Controller for Signup page, handles user creating the account
SlideSearchController
Controller for SlideSearch page, where user view slideshow when in search , list or delete accounts
SlideshowController
Controller for SlideShow page, where user view slideshow , list or delete accounts
Tag
Class that implements the logic of creating , comparing and printing tags
User
Class that implements logic of how Users are created, modified, deleted , how tags, pictures and albums are added, modified or deleted by users
